ISLAMABAD, Jun 29 (APP):Special Assistant to Prime Minister on Social Protection and Poverty Alleviation, Dr Sania Nishtar Monday said the payments to the deserving persons under Ehsaas Emergency Cash Programme would continue after June 30, 2020.
In a tweet, Dr Nishtar said the payment process under the programme would continue till disbursement of financial assistance to the 16,163,000 lockdown affected peoples as per the set target.
